
Work-in-progress JQuery plugin for creating particle effects on a canvas element, for use by humans.

Demo: http://bubblr-demo.heroku.com/

# Usage

Apply the following to any canvas element. Plugin will auto detect whether the browser supports canvases or not and will not start the bubbles!

    $(element).bubblr();


# Current Options

* numberOfBubbles (default 10)
* backgroundColor (default "transparent")
* bubbleColor (default "White")
* bubbleOpacity (default .7)
* bubbleMinSize (default 1)
* bubbleMaxSize (default 2)
* bubbleMaxSpeed (default 2)
* bubbleMinSpeed (default 1)
* animationSpeed (default 10)


# Future development

* Bubble direction / starting position